          Shed the nerves and do what you came to do!  When you're done performing the DJ will move you out of that queue and others can rate the performance with Shareaoke's simple rating system.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="media" align="left">
        <div class="media-left">
          <a href="#">
            <%= image_tag "Repeat.png", :height => '70px', :width => '70px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="media-left">
          <h4 class="media-heading">Repeat</h4>
          Nuff said, Superstar. It's now your world...and we're all just livin' in it.
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
